(ns farsund.data.ui
  (:require [reagent.core :as r]
            [reagent.ratom :refer [reaction]]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.encore :as e]
            [oops.core :refer [oget oget+]]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]
            [mui.core :as mui]
            [mui.colors :as colors]
            [farsund.flex :as flex]
            [farsund.utils.core :as u]

            ["react-virtualized/dist/commonjs/AutoSizer" :default AutoSizer]
            ["react-window" :refer [FixedSizeList FixedSizeGrid]]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Add" :default AddIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Remove" :default RemoveIcon]
            ["@material-ui/icons/Delete" :default DeleteIcon]))


(defn card-info [product]
  (let [pace-period (rf/subscribe [:data/pace-period])]
    (fn [{:keys [id name ean sales optimal
                 qty order pace margin]}]
      [flex/vbox
       [flex/box {:size :auto}
        [mui/typography {:align   :center
                         :variant :subtitle2}
         name]]
       [flex/box {:size  :auto
                  :style {:margin-bottom 16}}
        [mui/typography {:align :center}
         ean]]
       [flex/hbox {:style {:margin-bottom 16}}
        [flex/vbox {:size  1
                    :style {:padding-right 8}}
         [flex/hbox
          [flex/box {:size 2}
           [mui/typography {:variant :subtitle2} "tempo"]]
          [flex/box {:size            1
                     :justify-content :flex-end}
           [mui/typography (case @pace-period
                             "day" (.toFixed pace 1)
                             "weekday" (.toFixed (* 7 pace) 0)
                             "month" (.toFixed (* 30 pace) 0))]]]
         [flex/hbox
          [flex/box {:size 2}
           [mui/typography {:variant :subtitle2} "stan"]]
          [flex/box {:size            1
                     :justify-content :flex-end}
           [mui/typography (.toFixed qty 3)]]]]
        [flex/vbox {:size  1
                    :style {:padding-left 8}}
         [flex/hbox
          [flex/box {:size 2}
           [mui/typography {:variant :subtitle2} "marża"]]
          [flex/box {:size            1
                     :justify-content :flex-end}
           [mui/typography (.toFixed (* margin 100) 3)]]]
         [flex/hbox
          [flex/box {:size 2}
           [mui/typography {:variant :subtitle2} "optymalny"]]
          [flex/box {:size            1
                     :justify-content :flex-end}
           [mui/typography (.toFixed optimal 3)]]]]]])))


(defn card-supply-days [id supply-days]
  [flex/vbox {:size 1}
   [flex/box {:justify-content :center}
    [mui/typography {:align   :center
                     :variant :subtitle2}
     "zapas na dni"]]
   [flex/hbox {:height      48
               :align-items :center}
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-supply-days
                                                id (dec supply-days)])}
      [:> RemoveIcon]]]
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :max-width       "50px"
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/input {:type              :number
                 :value             supply-days
                 :disable-underline true
                 :on-change         #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-supply-days
                                                   id (u/elem->val %)])
                 :style             {:max-width "50px"}
                 :inputProps        {:style {:text-align :center}}}]]
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-supply-days
                                                id (inc supply-days)])}
      [:> AddIcon]]]]])


(defn card-order [id order]
  [flex/vbox {:size 1}
   [flex/box {:justify-content :center}
    [mui/typography {:align   :center
                     :variant :subtitle2}
     "zamówić"]]
   [flex/hbox {:height      48
               :align-items :center}
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-qty id (dec order)])}
      [:> RemoveIcon]]]
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :max-width       "50px"
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/input {:type              :number
                 :value             order
                 :disable-underline true
                 :on-change         #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-qty id (u/elem->val %)])
                 :style             {:max-width "50px"}
                 :inputProps        {:style {:text-align :center}}}]]
    [flex/box {:size            1
               :justify-content :center}
     [mui/icon-button {:on-click #(rf/dispatch [:data/change-market-order-qty id (inc order)])}
      [:> AddIcon]]]]])


(defn card-inputs [product]
  (let []
    (fn [product]
      (let [{:keys [id qty pace order]} product
            supply-days (e/round1 (/ (+ (max 0 qty) order) pace))]
        [flex/hbox
         [card-supply-days id supply-days]
         [card-order id order]]))))


(defn mobile-card [style index]
  (let [product (rf/subscribe [:data/market-order.search.nth index])
        updating? (rf/subscribe [:data/search-updating?])
        md>=? (rf/subscribe [:window/>=md?])]
    (fn [style index]
      (when @product
        [flex/box {:style style}
         [mui/paper {:style {:width   "350px"
                             :height  "200px"
                             :margin  :auto
                             :padding 16}}
          [flex/vbox
           [card-info @product]
           [card-inputs @product]]
          (when (and @updating? md>=?)
            [mui/circular-progress {:size  96
                                    :style {:position :absolute
                                            :top      "50%"
                                            :left     "50%"
                                            :margin   -48}}])]]))))

  @(rf/subscribe [:data/market-order])
  )

(comment
  (let [client-height @(rf/subscribe [:window/client-height])
        inner-width @(rf/subscribe [:window/inner-width])
        market-order-count @(rf/subscribe [:data/market-order.search.count])
        column-count (Math/floor (/ inner-width (min 366 (- inner-width 16))))
        row-count (Math/ceil (/ market-order-count column-count))]
    row-count)
  )

(defn mobile-page []
  (let [inner-width (rf/subscribe [:window/inner-width])
        inner-height @(rf/subscribe [:window/inner-height])
        market-order-count (rf/subscribe [:data/market-order.search.count])]
    (fn []
      (let [products-count @market-order-count]
        [flex/hbox {:height          "100%"
                    :justify-content :center
                    :style           {:overflow-y :hidden}}
         (let [height (- inner-height 112)
               width @inner-width]
           (println :height height
                    (.-height (.-visualViewport js/window)))
           (r/as-element
             (let [column-count (Math/floor (/ width (min 366 (- @inner-width 16))))
                   row-count (Math/ceil (/ products-count column-count))
                   screen-count (* column-count (Math/floor (/ height 256)))]
               [:> FixedSizeGrid {:column-count   (if (pos? width) column-count 0)
                                  :column-width   (if (pos? width) (/ width column-count) 0)
                                  :row-count      (if (pos? width) row-count 0)
                                  :row-height     (+ 200 16)
                                  :overscan-count (* 3 screen-count)
                                  :height         height
                                  :width          width
                                  :style          {:overflow-x :hidden}}
                (fn [params]
                  (let [column-index (oget params :columnIndex)
                        row-index (oget params :rowIndex)
                        index (+ (* row-index column-count) column-index)
                        style (js->clj (oget params :style))]
                    (r/as-element [mobile-card style index])))])))]))))

  (first @(rf/subscribe [:data/market-order]))
  )
